strapiEvent.name: Winter Pruning Class
strapiEvent.location: Botanical Garden of the Ozarks - Fayetteville, AR
strapiEvent.description:
Come to the garden and join Berni for a hands-on pruning class. Guests will not only learn about pruning trees in winter but we will also walk around the garden to see trees that need pruning and doing some pruning.

$15/members or $25/nonmembers
